object.customQuery: SELECT deductible.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, deductible.TypeCd as TypeCd, deductible.Value as Value, deductible.SystemId as SystemId, deductible.ParentId as ParentId FROM deductible where deductible.CMMContainer='Policy' and deductible.TypeCd='Amount'

SELECT distinct coverage.SystemId, coverage.ParentId, coverage.CMMContainer, coverage.Id, coverage.Status, coverage.CoverageCd, coverage.FullTermAmt, coverage.FullTermManualAmt, coverage.WrittenPremiumAmt, coverage.FinalPremiumAmt, coverage.EarnedAmt, coverage.AdditionalInd, coverage.OriginalCommissionPct, coverage.CommissionPct, coverage.ContributionPct, coverage.CommissionAmt, coverage.TransactionCommissionAmt, coverage.Description, coverage.PrevFinalAmt, coverage.PrevWrittenAmt, coverage.ShortRateAmt, coverage.CoinsurancePct, coverage.LapseInd, coverage.FutureStatusCd, coverage.ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd, coverage.ScheduledPremiumMod, coverage.NumberOfEmployees, coverage.NumberOfClass1Employees, coverage.InsideLimit, coverage.InsideDeductible, coverage.OutsideLimit, coverage.OutsideDeductible, coverage.PapersKeptInCd, coverage.DuplicateOffPremisesRecordsPct, coverage.EDPEquipmentLimit, coverage.EDPEquipmentInTransitLimit, coverage.EDPDataLimit, coverage.EDPMediaLimit, coverage.EDPDataAndMediaInTransitLimit, coverage.EDPBusinessIncomeLimit, coverage.EDPExtraExpenseLimit, coverage.FormType, coverage.NumberOfDays, coverage.NumberOfLocations, coverage.CoverageType, coverage.ClassificationRisk, coverage.EQNumberOfStories, coverage.EQRoofTankBuilding, coverage.EQSublimitPercentage, coverage.EQGradeDescription, coverage.EQMasonryVeneerLimit, coverage.EQBuildingConstruction, coverage.Location, coverage.StateRegistered, coverage.OtherLocationDesc, coverage.NumberOfPersons, coverage.OrdOrLawPercentage, coverage.FoodContaminationOption, coverage.RefrigerationMaintenanceInd, coverage.GURelatedExpensesLimit, coverage.GUIncreasedLossCostPct, coverage.GUExtPeriodOfRestoration, coverage.RetroactiveDate, coverage.Classification, coverage.MasonryVeneerPct, coverage.NumStories, coverage.DeductibleTier, coverage.RoofTank, coverage.OptionalIncreasedDeductible, coverage.NumLocations, coverage.NumberOfTrusts, coverage.NumberOfGolfCarts, coverage.AsstCareNumOfFacilities, coverage.RatingInd, coverage.AddedViaHOCov, coverage.RowId
from coverage 
join advrxxchangedbeans
on coverage.CMMContainer = advrxxchangedbeans.CMMContainer
and coverage.SystemId = advrxxchangedbeans.SystemId
where coverage.cmmcontainer in ('Policy', 'Application')
 and  concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' 
 and concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm) <='$$m_Enddt'
